stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Stopped: (no VMI)
  Stopped --> Pending: start VM
  Pending --> Scheduling: scheduling
  Scheduling --> Starting: scheduled
  Starting --> Running: boot complete
  Running --> Paused: pause
  Paused --> Running: unpause
  Running --> Stopping: stop VM
  Stopping --> Terminating: shutdown
  Terminating --> Stopped: cleanup
